  "doc_id": "27471",
  "text": "In our study, GFR ranged 33.5-135.8 m l/m in with a mean value of 77.5 ± 24.9 ml/min using SPSM, while using DPSM ranges 39.2-139.6 ml/min with mean GFR value of 36.8 ± 24.8 in obstructive uropathy group. The Gates in vivo [CITATION_1] method was considered feasible and very simple when compared to the plasma sampling method, which was a bit complex yet more accurate.",
